Download Mysid data table from database

nrp_download_mysid.Rd

Download Mysid data table from database

nrp_download_mysid(
  start_date = "2018-01-01",
  end_date = "2018-12-31",
  sites = NULL,
  parameters = "all",
  db_path = getOption("nrp.db_path", file.choose())
)

Arguments

start_date

The start date
end_date

The end date
sites

A character vector of the Site IDs
parameters

A character vector of the parameters to include. Permissible values can be found in the nrp::mysid_params
db_path

The SQLite connection object or path to the SQLite database

Value

CTD data table
